                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011202-76-off402 t18011202-76-cd403"></join>, forty-two yards of linen cloth, value 21s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18011202-76-victim640" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Evans
               <interp inst="t18011202-76-victim640" type="surname" value="Evans"></interp>
